{"tid":325292,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"寄生獸嘅劇情真係世界級","createTime":"2017-07-17T06:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T14:37:16.000Z","uid":342,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f75d69e58f5dc4b11403c019bf907bcfbb35537","tid":325292,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"一路都有人講但我一路都冇睇<br />\n<br />\n岩岩禁左套漫出黎睇<br />\n<br />\n啲劇情同jump啲戇鳩王道漫畫唔同不再講<br />\n<br />\n有好多位都好surprise<br />\n<br />\n要講嘅話真係要打千字文 我懶得打<br />\n<br />\n即係好似男主嘅心境變化<br />\n佢唔會講得好白 但又會比人睇到<br />\n感覺係 個男主變左 而你觀察到<br />\n而唔係其他漫畫咁同你講完 然後你知道男主變左<br />\n<br />\n總之呢套漫畫入面 好多漫畫嘅元素都好與別不同<br />\n啲人物好似真係存在係個個世界咁<br />\nsorry for1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e953b8dda18cfff475b83015f05e71a6ac3c47","tid":325292,"uid":54417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"以前啲動漫劇情好多都世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家成埋速食動漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0980350e4d4a6d17d6a73b2e80b43506c956ca15","tid":325292,"uid":54417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前啲動漫劇情好多都世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家成堆速食動漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5ad522e0d03a1ecd2775a713ed923d9f5215f699","tid":325292,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:46:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前啲動漫劇情好多都世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家成埋速食動漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n費事咁老屎忽先唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65a7d60fce739c97fd3975d2646d0c5adba229c","tid":325292,"uid":124192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:57:25.000Z","m